  Locus:
    Page: 159
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Fault
---
We are the makers of our own lives. There is no such thing as fate. Our
lives are the result of our previous actions, our karma, and it naturally
follows that, having been ourselves the makers of our karma, we must also
be able to unmake it.
